COMPONENTS
==========
  - PostgreSQL-native hybrid RAG engine (no Elasticsearch, no separate
    vector DB, no graph DB)
  - FastAPI server with `pip install hanimo-rag` deployment
  - Document upload + collection grouping + LLM connection
  - Production-ready search API

